  "description": "Use when implementing or troubleshooting the Salesforce Data Cloud Ingestion API \u2014 covers streaming ingestion (near-real-time micro-batches), bulk ingestion (CSV-based full-replace jobs), schema management in OpenAPI 3.0.x YAML, Connected App setup with cdp_ingest_api scope, and error handling for both modes. NOT for standard Salesforce Bulk API, CRM Analytics data import, or Data Cloud data streams from CRM objects.",
